name: Before One Week Of The Completion Of Three Years Period
query:
select 
        employee,
        deposit_amount,
        date_of_joining,
        quarterly_duration,
        interest_amount,
        department,
        location,
        rate_of_interest,
        total_amount,
        before_one_week
    from
`tabEmployee Security Deposit Register`
report_name: Before One Week Of The Completion Of Three Years Period
